subproject.corporate outcome: Capacities of national and local institutions enhanced to scale up proven MDG acceleration interventions and to plan, monitor, report and evaluate the MDG progress in the context of related national development priorities
subproject.description: The project aims at strengthening the national capacity to coordinate the national response to HIV/AIDs and enhance access to healhcare services for vulnerable groups; supporting initiatives where vulnerable groups enjoy greater access to information and support services for HIV/AIDS/STI prevention; strengthening capacities of key staff of health care system and AIDS Centers.
subproject.gender code: Gender Equality as a principal objective
subproject.title: HIV Prevention
